      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HERE COMES FOXY (1) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 0.8 lengths away in second (18.58) behind INFRARED POWER at this track. Top prospect. MISH MASH (2) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing third and beaten 1.5 lengths (18.65) behind INFRARED POWER at this track. Expected to be in the finish again. INFRARED POWER (5) was unfancied last time out but hit the ground running to lead all the way, scoring by 0.8 lengths (18.54) at this track in a Grade 3/4 over 312m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from six starts. Expecting another bold showing. SILVERSMITH (8) is another with top-three prospects.",
